        ''' chromosomes To show Is one Of them. You can list them
        '''
        ''' ```
        ''' hs1;hs2;hs3;hs4
        ''' ```
        ''' 
        ''' Or provide a regular expression that selects them based On a successful match
        ''' 
        ''' ```
        ''' /hs[1-4]$/
        ''' ```
        ''' 
        ''' The ``$`` anchor Is necessary, otherwise chromosomes Like *hs10, hs11 And
